casebody.data:
Gina CIMINO
v.
Joseph CIMINO Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided October 25, 2017

Gina Cimino, self-represented, in support of the petition.

The plaintiff's petition for certification to appeal from the Appellate Court, 174 Conn.App. 1, 164 A.3d 787 (2017), is denied.

ROGERS, C.J., did not participate in the consideration of or decision on this petition.
